Paper: hep-th/9904175

Date: 1999-04-26

Title: World-Volume Locally Supersymmetric Born-Infeld Actions

Authors: Bj\"orn Brinne, Svend E. Hjelmeland and Ulf Lindstr\"om

Comments: LaTeX, 14 pages, typos corrected, references and some remarks added

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B459 (1999) 507-514

We derive manifestly locally supersymmetric extensions of the Born-Infeldaction with $p=2$. The construction is based on a first order bosonic actionfor $Dp$-branes with a generalized Weyl invariance.